<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-76894" src="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-745x497.jpg" alt="Rigid Harley Sportster 1200 by Mika Motorcycles" width="745" height="497" srcset="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-745x497.jpg 745w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-420x280.jpg 420w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-180x120.jpg 180w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-768x512.jpg 768w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-570x380.jpg 570w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-135x90.jpg 135w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-1200x801.jpg 1200w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-258x172.jpg 258w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-360x240.jpg 360w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-720x480.jpg 720w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-275x183.jpg 275w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-150x100.jpg 150w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200.jpg 1490w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" /><br />
<span class="lede">Earlier this week,</span> we waxed lyrical about the enduring appeal of the Harley-Davidson Evolution Sportster while profiling David Zemla&#8217;s brat style-inspired <a href="https://www.bikeexif.com/harley-xlh-883" target="_blank" rel="noopener">XLH 883</a>. Now, a builder on the other side of the world has built a rigid Harley Sportster in a radically different style—further proving the Sporty&#8217;s incredible versatility.</p>
<p>This drag-style 2010 <a href="https://www.bikeexif.com/tag/sportster-1200" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sportster 1200</a> is the work of Mika Motorcycles, based in Depok, Indonesia. Shop founder Hery got his start by buying and selling secondhand Sportsters, and runs the enthusiast Instagram account <a href="https://www.instagram.com/sportster_attack/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sportster Attack</a>. His workshop is full of two things; used Sporties waiting to be customized, and exotic wheels that he loves to collect.<span id="more-76884"></span></p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-76899" src="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-1-745x497.jpg" alt="Rigid Harley Sportster 1200 by Mika Motorcycles" width="745" height="497" srcset="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-1-745x497.jpg 745w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-1-420x280.jpg 420w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-1-180x120.jpg 180w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-1-570x380.jpg 570w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-1-135x90.jpg 135w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-1-1200x801.jpg 1200w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-1-258x172.jpg 258w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-1-720x480.jpg 720w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-1-275x183.jpg 275w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-1-150x100.jpg 150w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-1.jpg 1490w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" /><br />
“I love hunting for rare rims,” Hery tells us. “It&#8217;s my challenge. I love to build <a href="https://www.bikeexif.com/tag/harley-davidson-sportster" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sportsters</a> with a racing touch, using classic Henry Abe, Kimtab, Morris, RC Components, and American Racing wheels.”</p>
<p>The breathtaking snowflake wheels on this build are cast alloy items from Italy dating back to the 1970s. They&#8217;re the same design that MV Agusta used on the 350 Ipotesi—the first Italian production bike with alloy wheels and three disc brakes. Hery modified them to fit the Harley, using a custom center-lock axle for the front wheel.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-76895" src="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-2-745x497.jpg" alt="Rigid Harley Sportster 1200 by Mika Motorcycles" width="745" height="497" srcset="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-2-745x497.jpg 745w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-2-420x280.jpg 420w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-2-180x120.jpg 180w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-2-570x380.jpg 570w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-2-135x90.jpg 135w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-2-1200x801.jpg 1200w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-2-258x172.jpg 258w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-2-360x240.jpg 360w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-2-720x480.jpg 720w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-2-275x183.jpg 275w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-2-150x100.jpg 150w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-2.jpg 1490w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" /><br />
An 18” M&amp;H Racemaster slick wraps around the rear wheel, with a 19” Shinko E240 tire at the opposite end. But the wheels only tell part of the story. Aiming for a barebones drag bike aesthetic, Hery repackaged the Sportster&#8217;s engine into a bespoke rigid frame.</p>
<p>With just a single disc brake at the back and nothing to slow the front down, it really is stripped down to the bare essentials. A small Mooneyes Cole Foster headlight is mounted to the forks by way of a custom bracket, bolted to where the caliper used to be. The taillight sits just behind the rear axle, adjacent to a pair of custom brake brackets.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-76896" src="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-3-745x745.jpg" alt="Rigid Harley Sportster 1200 by Mika Motorcycles" width="745" height="745" srcset="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-3-745x745.jpg 745w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-3-420x420.jpg 420w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-3-768x768.jpg 768w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-3-380x380.jpg 380w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-3-90x90.jpg 90w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-3-1200x1200.jpg 1200w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-3-360x360.jpg 360w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-3-720x720.jpg 720w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-3-275x275.jpg 275w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-3-150x150.jpg 150w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-3.jpg 1490w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" /><br />
A generous fairing adorns the front end, hand-shaped out of aluminum and trimmed with a slim yellow windscreen. Hery fabricated the aluminum tail section too, and added a slim diamond-stitched seat. The entire arrangement is remarkably elegant, echoing the aesthetics of vintage race bikes.</p>
<p>A Mooneyes oil tank is tucked beneath the seat, with a custom battery tray mounted lower down on the left side. Small cutouts on either side of the fairing offer space for the brake pedal and gear shifter to move freely.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-76897" src="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-4-745x497.jpg" alt="Rigid Harley Sportster 1200 by Mika Motorcycles" width="745" height="497" srcset="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-4-745x497.jpg 745w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-4-420x280.jpg 420w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-4-180x120.jpg 180w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-4-570x380.jpg 570w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-4-135x90.jpg 135w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-4-1200x801.jpg 1200w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-4-258x172.jpg 258w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-4-360x240.jpg 360w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-4-720x480.jpg 720w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-4-275x183.jpg 275w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-4-150x100.jpg 150w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-4.jpg 1490w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" /><br />
The engine hasn&#8217;t been neglected either. Hery rebuilt it with Wiseco pistons and a Daytona Twin Tec ignition. Other modifications include a Mikuni HSR42 carb, a chain conversion, and Mooneyes derby and cam covers.</p>
<p>The stubby slash-cut exhausts are original Mika Motorcycles parts, as are the relocated foot controls and their mounting plates.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-76901" src="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-5-745x497.jpg" alt="Rigid Harley Sportster 1200 by Mika Motorcycles" width="745" height="497" srcset="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-5-745x497.jpg 745w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-5-420x280.jpg 420w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-5-180x120.jpg 180w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-5-570x380.jpg 570w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-5-135x90.jpg 135w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-5-1200x801.jpg 1200w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-5-258x172.jpg 258w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-5-360x240.jpg 360w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-5-720x480.jpg 720w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-5-275x183.jpg 275w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-5-150x100.jpg 150w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-5.jpg 1490w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" /><br />
Additional parts include custom-made bars that mount directly to the original riser holes, underneath the top yoke, and grips from Owl in Japan. Other than a speedo, and the throttle and clutch controls, the cockpit area is pretty sparse.</p>
<p>Hery called in <a href="https://www.instagram.com/werspaint" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Wer&#8217;s Paint</a> to add a splash of red to the bike, opting for a gold finish on the wheels and clear-coated aluminum for the fairing and tail. The tank wears a pair of beat-up Harley-Davidson badges and a Mooneyes gas cap.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-76898" src="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-6-745x497.jpg" alt="Rigid Harley Sportster 1200 by Mika Motorcycles" width="745" height="497" srcset="https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-6-745x497.jpg 745w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-6-420x280.jpg 420w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-6-180x120.jpg 180w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-6-570x380.jpg 570w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-6-135x90.jpg 135w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-6-1200x801.jpg 1200w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-6-258x172.jpg 258w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-6-360x240.jpg 360w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-6-720x480.jpg 720w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-6-275x183.jpg 275w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-6-150x100.jpg 150w, https://kickstart.bikeexif.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/rigid-harley-sportster-1200-6.jpg 1490w" sizes="(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px" /><br />
Not quite a <a href="https://www.bikeexif.com/tag/cafe-racer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">café racer</a> and not quite a <a href="https://www.bikeexif.com/tag/drag-bike" target="_blank" rel="noopener">drag racer</a>, it&#8217;s hard to pigeonhole Mika Motorcycles&#8217; rigid Harley Sportster. So perhaps it&#8217;s best to take advice from the slogan that&#8217;s emblazoned on the side of the fairing; “Stop thinking, start chopping.”</p>
<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/mikamotorcycles" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mika Motorcycles Instagram</a> | Images by <a href="https://www.instagram.com/trialfy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Alfi Nuri</a></p>
